  {
    "id": "259384468",
    "title": "Special March Meetup!!",
    "eventUrl": "https://www.meetup.com/mumbai-women-coders/events/259384468/",
    "description": "As March is here, we are ready with our speakers!!\nWe hope you all had lovely Women's Day Celebration and if not don't worry, we are coming up with power pack, empowering event. The main aim of this meetup along with knowledge sharing will be pampering each other, lifting each other up and yes lots of fun. And if you want to add something more please share your ideas as well.\nWe really want to thanks Women Techmaker for sponsoring the food and goodies!!\nSo let'us begin with our amazing stack of speakers,\n1. Zeel Mehta\nTopic: Give it back! We will start with NPM first ;)\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/Zeel52086084\n\n2. Sanchita Mishra\nTopic: TDD\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/sanchim12\n\n3. Tanvi Sawant\nTopic: Move out of your Daily routine\n\n4. Disha Mourya, Preeti Wadhawani , Dipti Gandhi\nTopic: Rewinding!!\nTwitter: Disha - https://twitter.com/disha4mourya\nPreeti - https://twitter.com/pwadhwani2592\nDipti - https://twitter.com/mellowdipti",
