    "eventUrl": "https://www.meetup.com/mumbai-women-coders/events/258288383/",
    "description": "Hello Dear Members,\n\nWe are so glad to announce our that we are ready to organize the February meetup with our amazing set of speakers, who are very excited to share there knowlegde on our plarform. So come join us and make this event super exciting by being there. So our Speakers are\n1. Nikita Gandhi :- Deep dive into Flutter\nTwitter:@nikkitagandhi\n2. Priyanka Sabhagani :- Are you a mobile dev? Confused between react native, flutter or native? You're at the right place!!!\nTwitter : @PSabhagani\n3. Rashi Desai :- Design for Business: Sales Prediction by UX Usability\nTwitter: @rpdesai24\n4. Pranita Khaire :- Intro to Data Science!!\nTwitter :@PranitaKhaire\n\nSo please fill out the form for the march meetup!!\nhttps://goo.gl/forms/2Pqhc6E9oSPfiOPI3",
