    "id": "253335581",
    "title": "Workshop for August!!",
    "eventUrl": "https://www.meetup.com/mumbai-women-coders/events/253335581/",
    "description": "Want to get hands on React Native with passionate people building multi-platform products?\nPreeti is here to save the day! A experienced dev, who has handled complete dev cycles with a previous expertise in Android, is now here to guide you on React Native with a workshop! Also this workshop wouldn't be possible without our venue partner 91Springboard Mumbai!!!\nSign up to learn how to build beautiful apps for both Android and iOS.\nWe'll be covering the following:\n1. Basics: Props, state, components, JSX, images, debugging\n2. Layouts with Flexbox, listviews\n3. Async operations like network calls\n4. Protips and gotchas",
